{
  "stem": "1338.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, he's talking to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was so pathologically anti-Semitic that he couldn't even separate that discussion from the fact he was talking to a Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, I cannot obviously-- certainly, he was no great philosopher either.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, apparently, I'm just trying to show the relationship between people, and what kind of friends you pick up, and enemies, [LAUGHS] and in between.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was also responsible for fixing my leg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Serge, of course, remained my very, very close friend for the rest of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by time of the liquidation of Dora, because the Americans were coming in, I could-- I hear the tanks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could hear the fire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were trying to run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for four days, we were marched to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Dora.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the four days-- since I think I was asked the question here, who is an SS and who isn't, and are there any nice SS?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Certainly not who volunteered to SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was in a group that was marched.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by that time, they were already mobilizing the old men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This guy must have been over 50, and marched next to me-- not marched.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, he was in charge of the column we were marching.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were shooting people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were killing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The young SS were running around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If somebody was dragging or something, they-- they will kill him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember we came across a dead horse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody jumped on it and started grabbing the meat and eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I learned from the French prisoners how to eat dandelions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's a French delicacy, raw dandelions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's something else.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I learned from the Russian how to wash in snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Take your clothes and roll in snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
